---
// Por qué elegirnos — El Buen Gusto
// 6 puntos con iconos animados
---

<section id="porque" class="relative py-20 md:py-28 bg-ebg-crema overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Trazos gestuales -->
  <svg class="absolute top-16 left-8 w-20 md:w-28 opacity-50 pointer-events-none" viewBox="0 0 100 60" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
    <path d="M 5 30 L 90 30" stroke="#FF7D0E" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
    <path d="M 10 45 Q 30 35, 50 45" stroke="#FF7D0E" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
  </svg>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto reveal">
      <span class="inline-block font-display text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-ebg-naranja-oscuro font-semibold mb-4">
        Por qué nosotros
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl text-ebg-negro leading-tight">
        Tradición renovada, <span class="text-ebg-naranja italic">cada día</span>.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de diferenciales -->
    <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 md:gap-6">
      <!-- 1 - Sabores de rellenos -->
      <div class="reveal group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border border-ebg-negro/5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-ebg-naranja/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="ebg-icon-box bg-ebg-naranja/10 text-ebg-naranja">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" class="ebg-icon-svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="8" y="8" width="32" height="32" rx="3" />
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="3" fill="currentColor" />
            <path d="M 14 14 L 16 16 M 32 14 L 34 16 M 14 32 L 16 34 M 32 32 L 34 34" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebg-negro mt-5 mb-2">Más de 30 sabores</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-ebg-negro/70 leading-relaxed">De rellenos para que siempre tengas algo nuevo para probar.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2 - Artesanal -->
      <div class="reveal group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border border-ebg-negro/5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-ebg-naranja/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="ebg-icon-box bg-ebg-naranja/10 text-ebg-naranja">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" class="ebg-icon-svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M 8 30 Q 16 22, 24 30 T 40 30" />
            <path d="M 8 36 Q 16 28, 24 36 T 40 36" />
            <circle cx="12" cy="14" r="2" fill="currentColor" />
            <circle cx="22" cy="12" r="2" fill="currentColor" />
            <circle cx="32" cy="14" r="2" fill="currentColor" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebg-negro mt-5 mb-2">100% artesanal</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-ebg-negro/70 leading-relaxed">Pastas frescas elaboradas a diario con el oficio de siempre.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3 - Materias primas -->
      <div class="reveal group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border border-ebg-negro/5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-ebg-naranja/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="ebg-icon-box bg-ebg-naranja/10 text-ebg-naranja">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" class="ebg-icon-svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M 24 6 L 24 42" />
            <path d="M 24 12 Q 18 14, 16 20 M 24 12 Q 30 14, 32 20" />
            <path d="M 24 22 Q 18 24, 16 30 M 24 22 Q 30 24, 32 30" />
            <path d="M 24 32 Q 18 34, 16 40 M 24 32 Q 30 34, 32 40" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebg-negro mt-5 mb-2">Materias primas premium</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-ebg-negro/70 leading-relaxed">Cuidadosamente seleccionadas para que cada bocado lo sientas.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 4 - Tecnología -->
      <div class="reveal group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border border-ebg-negro/5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-ebg-naranja/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="ebg-icon-box bg-ebg-naranja/10 text-ebg-naranja">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" class="ebg-icon-svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M 24 8 L 24 40" />
            <path d="M 12 16 L 36 32 M 12 32 L 36 16" />
            <path d="M 24 8 L 20 12 M 24 8 L 28 12" />
            <path d="M 24 40 L 20 36 M 24 40 L 28 36" />
            <path d="M 12 16 L 16 16 L 14 12 M 36 16 L 32 16 L 34 12" />
            <path d="M 12 32 L 16 32 L 14 36 M 36 32 L 32 32 L 34 36" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebg-negro mt-5 mb-2">Tecnología de conservación</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-ebg-negro/70 leading-relaxed">Para mantener la frescura y el sabor de cada producto.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 5 - Opciones -->
      <div class="reveal group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border border-ebg-negro/5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-ebg-naranja/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="ebg-icon-box bg-ebg-naranja/10 text-ebg-naranja">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" class="ebg-icon-svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="6" y="14" width="10" height="20" rx="2" />
            <rect x="19" y="14" width="10" height="20" rx="2" />
            <rect x="32" y="14" width="10" height="20" rx="2" />
            <path d="M 11 20 L 11 28 M 24 20 L 24 28 M 37 20 L 37 28" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebg-negro mt-5 mb-2">Frescas, congeladas, listas</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-ebg-negro/70 leading-relaxed">Tres formatos para que comer rico sea fácil todos los días.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 6 - Compra simple -->
      <div class="reveal group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border border-ebg-negro/5 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-ebg-naranja/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="ebg-icon-box bg-ebg-naranja/10 text-ebg-naranja">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" class="ebg-icon-svg" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="14" y="6" width="20" height="36" rx="3" />
            <path d="M 20 36 L 28 36" />
            <path d="M 18 12 L 30 12" />
            <circle cx="24" cy="20" r="3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebg-negro mt-5 mb-2">Compra simple</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-ebg-negro/70 leading-relaxed">Una experiencia renovada, pensada para que sea ágil y cuidada.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ebg-icon-box {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1), background-color 0.4s ease;
  }
  .ebg-icon-svg {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .group:hover .ebg-icon-box {
    transform: scale(1.08) rotate(-3deg);
    background-color: #FF7D0E;
    color: #FFF5EE;
  }
  .group:hover .ebg-icon-svg {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    animation: iconWiggle 0.6s ease-in-out;
  }
  @keyframes iconWiggle {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(0deg); }
    25% { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-6deg); }
    75% { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(6deg); }
  }
</style>
